{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011VUizdPTFLKDY93Ch2c4gx","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A v6\n     2→* Carefully balanced for Vov constraints at 500nA tail\n     3→\n     4→.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n     5→\n     6→* Input Pair (W=5u L=14u for low 1/f noise, same W/L≈0.36 for Vov>50mV at 250nA)\n     7→XM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=5u L=14u nf=1\n     8→XM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=5u L=14u nf=1\n     9→\n    10→* Tail (500nA)\n    11→XM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=3.8u L=4u nf=1\n    12→\n    13→* PMOS Fold (W=6u L=14u, same W/L≈0.43 for Vov>150mV, large area for low 1/f)\n    14→XM3  fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=6u L=14u nf=1\n    15→XM4  fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=6u L=14u nf=1\n    16→\n    17→* PMOS Bias Mirrors (very long L: ~25nA, still Vov>150mV)\n    18→XM12 fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=20u nf=1\n    19→XM13 fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=20u nf=1\n    20→\n    21→* PMOS Cascode (W=0.42u L=2u, Vov>150mV at ~250nA)\n    22→XM5  cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=2u nf=1\n    23→XM6  vout  vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=2u nf=1\n    24→\n    25→* NMOS Cascode (W=0.36u L=1u, Vov>50mV at ~269nA)\n    26→XM7  cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.36u L=1u nf=1\n    27→XM8  vout  vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.36u L=1u nf=1\n    28→\n    29→* NMOS Current Sources (large area for low 1/f noise, same W/L≈0.54)\n    30→XM9  src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=6u L=11u nf=1\n    31→XM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=6u L=11u nf=1\n    32→\n    33→.ends ota_foldcasc\n    34→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6266b8be-d841-435a-9255-91a835985639","uuid":"a6ee7352-934a-4229-8d0a-e4cf5d3a831d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10